      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This example features a 6-speed manual gearbox and has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and reinforcement of the rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity. The engine's individual throttle bodies deliver immediate throttle response, while the factory limited-slip differential provides excellent power delivery through the corners. Equipped with refreshed suspension bushings and Bilstein dampers, the chassis dynamics remain sharp. This is a driver-focused machine that prioritizes powertrain integrity and performance over showroom perfection.",
